the runes for ice comet drop quite a bit now.  I went through my runes in the bank the other day and made a ton of spells (including 4 copies of ice comet) which I have been selling in EC for the past few days for 100p each.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uspankda.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Spankda</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/13/01 3:22:39 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ice Comet?</span><hr size=1> I paid 500pp for my copy of Ice Comet, but I had the cash and I really wanted to make sure I had IC before 49.<br>
<br>
Research is 164 now and I need to up it, but I'm out of cash to do so.  I have two astral and about eight frost, so I could likely make it and sell it, but I'm keeping the astral for super nova if needed (I traded for that).<br>
<br>
Regardless, I have a personal aversion to *selling* research spells to fellow wizards.  When I get the chance, I make them for free.  I've made many copies of Circle of Force, at least one Gravity Flux, and one Paralyzing Earth for by brother and sister wizards.  <br>
<br>
Just a personal thing for me -- not selling spells to my wizard friends.  I have reaped benefits from the friends I've made this way, though. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uyofallien.showPublicProfile?language=EN>yofallien</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 7:50:06 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ice Comet?</span><hr size=1> /cheer Spanka<br>
